snippet.title: CONSUME ME (Build Ver 4 GAMEPLAY)
snippet.description:
CONSUME ME 
(DEVLOG: playconsume.me)

//////////////////////////

BUILD VERSION 4: 
- Complete “narrative” loop. 
- Narrative “interstitials” + vignettes. 
- Only one meal. 
- Randomly generated calorie budget and plate shapes. 

RULES / GUIDELINES: 
- Aim to fill the plate while staying under calorie budget. 
- Click to rotate food pieces. 
0 Food pieces should not be overlapping (I have not implemented this yet, but plan to do so in the near future). 

NOTES: 
- Right now, there are no penalties or consequences to only partially filling the plate, but eventually I’m planning to add a penalty if you do decide to leave the plate empty or only partially filled. 

//////////////////////////
Jenny Jiao Hsia 
www.qdork.com
@q_dork
